snippet.title: Chainsaw Warrior: Lords of the Night - Official Trailer
snippet.description: Chainsaw Warrior: Lords of the Night is a new chapter for Games Workshop's cult classic! Based on the original Chainsaw Warrior board game, this sequel adds new layers of intensity to the game's unique formula. Find out more at ChainsawWarrior.net
